item.description: × YISUNSHIN HD Wallpaper ❮ ❯ Chungmugong Yi Sun-shin was a famous general in an Asian kingdom. He was extremely loyal and of prowess. At the time when the nation was in danger, Yi Sun-shin built a powerful navy and created the iron armored 'turtle ship', making indelible contribution to Korea Kingdom for dominating around sea areas. 'Wherever iron turtle ships sail on, the sea areas belong to me.' said Yi.
